name: City Kids
description: A free, action-packed club for all Primary school children from Reception to Year 6. Games, Crafts, Quizzes, Prizes, Bible Stories and more!

name: Youth Growth Group
description: Weekly Growth Group for young people in school years 10-13

name: Fuel
description: Our Sunday morning Bible study group for young people in school years 7-9. We meet together to study & discuss the Bible, allow space to ask questions, seek to encourage one another, and pray.

name: The Furnace
description:
On Sunday evenings during term time, after the 6:30pm service, all our young people in year 7-13 are invited to join us for social time, snacks and prayer at a different Beeston venue each week.

On some weekends we'll have lunch after the morning service instead, keep an eye on our calendar to check when!
